text: Corynomalus elegans is a species of handsome fungus beetles in the subfamily Lycoperdininae. It is found in Ecuador. == References == == External links == * * Corynomalus elegans at insectoid.info Category:Beetles described in 1902 Category:Endomychidae Category:Fauna of Ecuador Category:Taxa named by Ernő Csíki
